OL,3,CWRU makes decision on the sale of
OL,4,CCardiff Rugby
OL,6,FThe Welsh Rugby Union has reached a
OL,7,Fdecision over the sale of Cardiff
OL,8,FRugby, but the identity of the new
OL,9,Fowners is not yet being revealed.
OL,11,FAt a Union Board meeting today, the
OL,12,Frecommendations of the WRU Executive
OL,13,FTeam - led by CEO Abi Tierney and
OL,14,Fincluding Director of Rugby Dave
OL,15,FReddin - were considered.
OL,17,FA 'unanimous' decision has been made
OL,18,Fthis afternoon, with the result of the
OL,19,Fbidding process now due to be
OL,20,Fcommunicated to those involved and
OL,21,Fstaff at Cardiff.
