OL,6,FIn a statement, the WRU said: "The
OL,7,Fboard reviewed in detail the final two
OL,8,Fbids and unanimously approved the
OL,9,Fproposal to move forward with a
OL,10,Fpreferred bidder into an exclusivity
OL,11,Fperiod.
OL,13,F"Following this decision, the WRU has
OL,14,Fobligations to liaise with a number of
OL,15,Fstakeholders over the next few days.
OL,17,F"We will then discuss the decision
OL,18,Fwith the two bidders and the
OL,19,Fmanagement of Cardiff Rugby.
