OL,6,F"We expect to be in a position to have
OL,7,Fcompleted this by next week.
OL,9,F"The WRU hopes to finalise the
OL,10,Fdetailed negotiations with the
OL,11,Fpreferred bidder and sign a binding
OL,12,Fagreement within a matter of weeks."
OL,14,FThere have been two parties interested
OL,15,Fin acquiring the Arms Park outfit. One
OL,16,Fis a consortium led by former Cardiff
OL,17,FDirector Martyn Ryan, which includes
OL,18,Fthree Hollywood film producers.
