OL,3,CWRU makes decision on the sale of
OL,4,CCardiff Rugby
OL,6,FThe identity of the other bidder has
OL,7,Fbeen shrouded in secrecy but rumours
OL,8,Fclaim it is Y11, the owner of the
OL,9,FOspreys. Whilst this remains
OL,10,Funconfirmed, neither Y11 nor the
OL,11,Fregion themselves have denied the
OL,12,Frumours when given the opportunity in
OL,13,Frecent weeks.
OL,15,FA Y11 purchase of Cardiff would lead
OL,16,Fto the demise of the Ospreys as they
OL,17,Fare currently known. It would also
OL,18,Fpresent the WRU with the fastest and
OL,19,Feasiest route to reduce from four to
OL,20,Fthree professional sides in Wales, as
OL,21,Fis their preferred strategy.
