OL,3,CWRU makes decision on the sale of
OL,4,CCardiff Rugby
OL,6,FWhen ITV Wales asked WRU Chair Richard
OL,7,FCollier-Keywood if Y11 had bid for
OL,8,FCardiff before Christmas, he refused
OL,9,Fto confirm or deny.
OL,11,FThe WRU will now enter an 'exclusivity
OL,12,Fperiod' with the successful bidder.
OL,13,FThis means the Union can no longer
OL,14,Fnegotiate with other interested
OL,15,Fparties, while the buyer conducts due
OL,16,Fdiligence on both financial and legal
OL,17,Fmatters.
