OL,6,FIn April last year, Cardiff Rugby
OL,7,Fcollapsed into administration and was
OL,8,Frescued immediately by the Welsh Rugby
OL,9,FUnion, who have owned them ever since.
OL,11,FThe plan has always been for the club
OL,12,Fto return to private ownership and
OL,13,Fthat takes a step closer this evening.
